// (ObservedAsAlignmentTile (distribution (PhyloCTMCTile (tree (DrawTile (YuleTile (birthRate (AssignedArgumentTile (LiteralTile))) (taxa (AssignedArgumentTile (AlignmentTaxaTile (alignment (AssignedArgumentTile (AssignmentTile (FromNexusTile (file (AssignedArgumentTile (LiteralTile))))))))))))) (branchRateModel (StrictClockTile (rate (AssignedArgumentTile (LiteralTile))) (tree (AssignedArgumentTile (DrawTile (YuleTile (birthRate (AssignedArgumentTile (LiteralTile))) (taxa (AssignedArgumentTile (AlignmentTaxaTile (alignment (AssignedArgumentTile (AssignmentTile (FromNexusTile (file (AssignedArgumentTile (LiteralTile)))))))))))))))) (substitutionModel (JC69Tile)) (partialSiteRateModel (SiteModelTile (shape (AssignedArgumentTile (LiteralTile))) (numCategories (AssignedArgumentTile (LiteralTile))) (numSites (AssignedArgumentTile (LiteralTile))))))) (observation (AssignmentTile (FromNexusTile (file (AssignedArgumentTile (LiteralTile)))))))
